140
00:15:23,732 --> 00:15:29,007
And the first shot, after the title credits, confirms this impression.

141
00:15:29,007 --> 00:15:40,139
It is a panoramic shot from high above, Manhattan in the night, camera moving above the streets, accompanied by the sound of the kidnappers' prayers,

142
00:15:40,163 --> 00:15:48,478
as if the kidnappers stroll above the city, getting ready to descend on earth to ripe their deadly harvest.

143
00:15:49,282 --> 00:15:55,289
Similarly, there are no direct shots of the planes hitting the Twin Towers in World Trade Center.

144
00:15:55,860 --> 00:16:07,279
