629
01:00:59,860 --> 01:01:01,095
She was absolutely sincere.

630
01:01:01,540 --> 01:01:03,980
And I was really grateful.

631
01:01:04,040 --> 01:01:12,876
But you see, the paradox is that it was possible for her to say, you owe me no apology, only after I did apologize.

632
01:01:13,780 --> 01:01:14,875
And this is not hypocrisy.

633
01:01:15,260 --> 01:01:17,657
That's the mystery of communication.

