637
01:01:31,001 --> 01:01:33,558
This is how now you will say, what's the profit?

638
01:01:33,820 --> 01:01:40,994
The profit is respect, friendship, love, communication, through communication, through communication between us.

639
01:01:42,441 --> 01:01:42,791
