689
01:06:30,420 --> 01:06:31,310
You have a terrorist.

690
01:06:32,160 --> 01:06:37,338
You, instead of torturing him there, which would make you feel bad, you give him the pill.

691
01:06:37,701 --> 01:06:41,777
And the terrorist, suspected terrorist, just seems to take a half an hour nap.

692
01:06:42,201 --> 01:06:43,098
But then he awakens.

693
01:06:43,200 --> 01:06:45,293
And I confess everything you want, no?

694
01:06:46,580 --> 01:06:52,979
The first thing that bothers me here is that how this fits perfectly our postmodern logic of,

695
01:06:53,320 --> 01:06:56,536
which I develop in many of the books, of decaf coffee.

696
01:06:57,320 --> 01:07:00,918
We like today's projects, sorry, objects, products,

697
01:07:01,320 --> 01:07:03,057
without paying the price for them.

698
01:07:03,380 --> 01:07:05,059
Coffee, but decaf coffee.

699
01:07:05,201 --> 01:07:06,837
Beer, but beer without alcohol.

700
01:07:07,201 --> 01:07:08,799
A cake, but fat-free cake.

701
01:07:08,880 --> 01:07:11,096
And don't you think that this is only for products?

702
01:07:11,700 --> 01:07:16,856
I claim it's exactly the same in our intersubjective relations.

703
01:07:18,220 --> 01:07:22,080
Colin Powell's theory of war was precisely decaffeinated war.

704
01:07:22,200 --> 01:07:25,019
war, but no victims on our side.

705
01:07:25,180 --> 01:07:27,377
And to be a little bit more nasty,

706
01:07:27,820 --> 01:07:37,759
I would say that at least the way it is in its predominant form, multiculturalist tolerance is the tolerance of, to be nasty, the decaffeinated other.

707
01:07:37,981 --> 01:07:38,084
No?

708
01:07:38,661 --> 01:07:40,019
The other is abstracted.

709
01:07:40,100 --> 01:07:47,200
For example, I think this is the filthiest form of racism to celebrate Native Americans, if you call them that.

710
01:07:47,280 --> 01:07:53,999
I found this disgusting, even more racist than Indians, because I spoke with one of them, and he told me, Native Americans, what is this?

711
01:07:54,181 --> 01:07:55,080
Are we part of nature?

712
01:07:55,120 --> 01:07:56,635
What are you, cultural Americans?

713
01:07:57,100 --> 01:08:04,420
And he said, to be called an Indian, at least then my name is a monument to white men's stupidity.

714
01:08:04,480 --> 01:08:06,637
No, like, they thought better.

