That was the problem for him.

789
01:15:30,760 --> 01:15:37,459
I mean, it would be even obscene and racist to say for him, oh, we blacks want whites to tolerate us.

790
01:15:37,580 --> 01:15:44,795
You know, it's the same ridicule as to say, as if a eminist would have said, we want men to tolerate women.

791
01:15:45,460 --> 01:15:49,537
Which is even a very obscene idea, like many of my male friends would have said,

792
01:15:49,941 --> 01:15:53,740
