826
01:18:56,420 --> 01:19:00,619
So we can even say he's guilty for Hitler in a certain way.

827
01:19:00,780 --> 01:19:07,098
Because it was because of his political plotting that German was not unified earlier as a nation state.

828
01:19:07,400 --> 01:19:11,838
We all know this is what caused First World War and so on.

829
01:19:12,300 --> 01:19:13,371
Now, what is the shock?

830
01:19:14,320 --> 01:19:30,237
The shock is that the same person ordering tortures, poisoning, blah, was, in the evening, after his work was done, was writing the most precious of incredible depth mystical meditations.

831
01:19:30,561 --> 01:19:35,434
Absolutely, how should I put it in a vulgar way, top level, at the level of Santa Teresa, whoever you want.

